room_title: Escape room "The Not So Perfect Dinner Party" by MasterMind Escape the Room Game in Little Rock
room_address: 14710 Cantrell Rd a6, Little Rock, AR 72223
room_description: You have been invited to a dinner party by an old friend you haven’t seen in years by the name of Albus.When you all make it to the dinner party you walk inside and you begin to realize that Albus may not be the same guy that you knew from years ago. You want out! But you’ve noticed the doors and windows are locked. Will you make it out before the dinner is ready and Albus reveals what he has up his sleeve? You have 60 minutes, I hope you've brought your appetite!
